content: Man it‚Äôs a real problem. We have tried in vain to orange pill a bunch of our fellow farmers but they don‚Äôt want to listen. Instead they just keep financing with more debt year after year! Conversely we ran our farm 100% debt free from the very beginning (except for the mortgage) only adding infrastructure and production when we could afford to pay out of pocket. All excess was saved in Bitcoin. Five years in, we paid off our land and live freely, while our counterparts are struggling to even make ends meet and pay for loans they never should have taken out. It‚Äôs sad that people can literally be given a way out but aren‚Äôt willing to adapt their thinking and systems to create more sustainable alternatives for themselves and their families.
